headline: American Airlines Stock Has a New Bull, Thanks to a New Citi Card Deal
summary: American Airlines stock should get a boost in 2025 from several catalysts, including a new credit card deal with Citi, say Raymond James analysts.  The analysts also highlight an improved revenue outlook, a strong competitive strategy, and anecdotal evidence of better interactions with contracted customers.  A card deal with  Citi  can help  American Airlines Group  fly above estimates, Raymond James argued on Monday.
